history.title: Basic Greetings in French
history.notes:
Bonjour – Hello / Good morning

Bonsoir – Good evening
bonui-goodnight

Merci – Thank you

S’il vous plaît – Please

Au revoir – Goodbye

history.title: Wochentage (Days of the Week)
history.notes:
Montag – Monday

Dienstag – Tuesday

Mittwoch – Wednesday

Donnerstag – Thursday

Freitag – Friday

Samstag – Saturday

Sonntag – Sunday

history.title: Everyday Expressions
history.notes:
Ciao – Hello / Goodbye

Per favore – Please

Grazie – Thank you

Scusa – Excuse me

Buongiorno – Good morning
